# 📄 PRODUCT REQUIREMENTS DOCUMENT (FINAL)

## Smart Union Parishad Management System

---

# 🧠 1. OVERVIEW

A full-stack web application to digitize operations of a single Union Parishad in Bangladesh.

The system replaces manual processes with:

* Digital citizen registry
* Certificate generation system
* Holding tax enforcement
* Relief management
* Financial tracking
* Public verification

---

# 🎯 2. CORE OBJECTIVES

* Digitize all union services
* Enforce holding tax compliance
* Prevent fraud (QR verification)
* Improve operator efficiency
* Enable transparent governance

---

# 👥 3. USER ROLES

## Admin (Secretary)

* Approve certificates
* Manage users
* Manage templates
* Control system settings
* View reports

## Operator (Entrepreneur)

* Create citizens
* Issue services
* Collect tax
* Manage records

## Citizen

* View services
* Download certificates
* Track status

---

# 🧩 4. CORE FEATURES

---

## 4.1 Authentication

* JWT-based authentication
* bcrypt password hashing
* Role-based access control
* Permission system

---

## 4.2 Citizen Management

* Full CRUD
* Unique fields: NID, mobile
* Fields:
  name_bn, name_en, father_name, mother_name
  address, ward_no, holding_no
  income, occupation, landless, disability
* Profile with tabs:
  Info | Tax | Certificates | Relief

---

## 4.3 Holding Tax System (CRITICAL)

* Yearly tax records
* Unique: citizen_id + year
* Tax receipt generation

### Rules:

* If tax unpaid:

  * Block service application
  * Block certificate printing
* Admin can create but cannot print

---

## 4.4 Certificate System (CORE)

### Template-Based Engine

* Template with placeholders:
  {{name}}, {{father_name}}

### Workflow:

Draft → Submitted → Approved → LOCKED

### Rules:

* Editable before approval
* Immutable after approval
* No delete (soft delete only)

### Data:

* reference_no (unique)
* final_text
* data_snapshot
* pdf_url

---

## 4.5 Certificate Design (Government Style)

* A4 layout
* Header:
  Government title + Union name
* Body:
  Bangla text
* Footer:
  Signature + QR + reference number
* Watermark

---

## 4.6 QR Verification System

* QR contains:
  verification URL (/verify/[reference_no])

### Public Page:

* Show valid / invalid
* Display summary

---

## 4.7 Relief Program System

### Flow:

Create → Criteria → Auto Generate → Review → Approve → LOCK

### Features:

* Criteria filtering:
  income, ward, landless
* Prevent duplicate beneficiaries

---

## 4.8 Financial System (Cashbook)

* Track all income:
  tax, certificate fees
* Reports:
  daily, monthly, operator-wise

---

## 4.9 Audit Log (CRITICAL)

Track all actions:

* user_id
* action
* target_id
* timestamp
* ip

---

## 4.10 Global Search

Search across:

* citizens
* certificates
* reference numbers

---

## 4.11 Excel Import/Export

* Import citizens
* Export reports

---

## 4.12 Notification System

Alerts:

* Tax unpaid
* Pending approvals

---

## 4.13 Public Portal

Citizen can:

* Login
* View certificates
* Download PDF
* Verify certificate

---

## 4.14 Print System

* Print preview
* Print history

### Rule:

* Block print if tax unpaid

---

## 4.15 Settings Panel

Admin can configure:

* Union name
* Logo
* Signature
* Certificate format

